/*Question ->
  
In this challenge we are drow a patern Patern is like this
  
****
***
**
*


Explain ->  We use to for loops first loops start with 4 and go up to 0,and decrement the value of i
             and the second loop start with 1 and go up to i.And increment the value of j
             After the value of i  we give a new line .

*/    


Solution->
  
  public class Patterns_5_ {
  public static void main(String[] args) {
    for(int i=4; i>=0; i--){
    for(int j=1; j<=i; j++ ){
      System.out.print("*");
    }
    System.out.println();
  }
  }
  }
  }
    
